query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND pi.note not like '%Erin Bates%' AND pi.note not like '%Federica Stradi%' AND (cn.name like '%New Line Cinema%' OR cn.name like '%Universal Pictures%' OR cn.name like '%Legendary%' OR cn.name like '%Focus Features%') AND cn.country_code in ('cshh','tm','bb') AND it3.info in ('languages','books','LD video standard','rating','LD release date','LD disc format','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','LD video quality','LD label','trivia','LD additional information','LD analog right','LD number') AND (rt.role like '%Felicia D. Henderson%' OR rt.role like '%MF%' OR rt.role like '%Mike Martin%') AND (chn.name like '%Groot%' OR chn.name like '%Jack Torrance%') AND k.keyword not like '%police%' AND k.keyword not like '%love%' AND k.keyword not like '%escape%' AND k.keyword not like '%romance%' AND k.keyword not like '%betrayed%'
